The 12th Filmfare Awards were held in 1965. Satyen Bose's Dosti was the biggest winner on the night, winning the Best Film award among a few other wins. Raj Kapoor won the Best Director award for Sangam and Vyjayanthimala won her Best Actress trophy for the same film. Dosti Raj Kapoor - Sangam Dilip Kumar - Leader Vyjayanthimala - Sangam Nana Palsikar - Shehar Aur Sapna Nirupa Roy - Shehnai Dosti - Bani Bhatt Dosti - Govind Moonis Dosti - Laxmikant-Pyarelal Dosti - Majrooh Sultanpuri for Chahoonga Main Tujhe Dosti - Mohammad Rafi for Chahoonga Main Tujhe Kohra Jahan Ara Woh Kaun Thi? Geet Gaya Pattharon Ne Sangam Sangam http://www.imdb.com/event/ev0000245/1965/
I read the paragraph on http://wikipedia.org
